《'''靈魂餐廳'''》（{{lang-en|'''Soul Kitchen'''}}）是2009年由[[法提·阿金|法提·阿金]]執導的喜劇電影，本片獲選為[[威尼斯影展|第66屆威尼斯影展]]正式競賽片，並獲得[[威尼斯影展評審團特別獎|評審團特別獎]]。<ref>{{cite news | first =  | last =  | title = Official Awards | work = la Biennale di Venezia | date = 2009-09-12 | url = http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/festival/premi/awards.html?back=true | accessdate = 2009-09-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090922185137/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/festival/premi/awards.html?back=true | archivedate = 2009-09-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2010/09/06/100906crci_cinema_lane | title=Slice and Dice | work=The New Yorker | author=Anthony Lane | date=2010-09-06 | accessdate=2010-11-10 | archive-date=2012-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020093003/http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2010/09/06/100906crci_cinema_lane | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 劇情 ==
住在漢堡的日諾經營一家餐廳「靈魂餐廳」，女友打定主意遠赴上海工作；原本不想離開德國的日諾最終也耐不住思念，決定把餐廳經營權交給還在坐牢假釋的哥哥，而餐廳又因為非常性格的主廚每天變化菜色，加上現場有音樂表演而變得越來越火紅，人滿為患，沒想到日諾以前的同學開始千方百計想要買下餐廳。

